WEBVTT

00:02:59.913 --> 00:03:02.538
and some people thought I was crazy,

00:03:02.538 --> 00:03:05.621
and I had a really hard time
getting research funding.

00:03:05.621 --> 00:03:07.079
But I persevered,

00:03:08.204 --> 00:03:12.038
and I eventually conducted
some experiments deep in the forest,

00:03:12.079 --> 00:03:13.496
25 years ago.

00:03:14.121 --> 00:03:16.996
I grew 80 replicates of three species:

00:03:17.038 --> 00:03:20.204
paper birch, Douglas fir,
and western red cedar.

00:03:20.246 --> 00:03:24.288
I figured the birch and the fir
would be connected in a belowground web,

00:03:24.329 --> 00:03:25.579
but not the cedar.

00:03:25.579 --> 00:03:27.121
It was in its own other world.

00:03:28.454 --> 00:03:30.288
And I gathered my apparatus,